description:
It felt like it was time for another totally random Hearthstone video, so here it is. In this episode we finish up an Arena run with the best Druid deck I have ever drafted.

I tried to hover over all the cards as I played, so just pause the video if you are new to the game and want to read what they do.

TwitchTV: http://www.twitch.tv/ethotv/videos
